Description:
You come across a zingarian cart, when you approach it an old woman appears and says to you:

"Hello travelers, would you fancy playing a card game with me? It is a very special game in which I will show you four possible cards that describe your future, then all you have to do is try to guess which one suits you best.

Also, if you feel brave and want to take risks, I can try to improve the possible outcomes.
DescriptionAction: And remember... fortune favors the brave!"
